data.description: Move-in ready home! This beautiful home is nestled in the heart of Tracy close to schools, Sutter Tracy Hospital & most importantly easy access to 11th Street for all commuters to Bay Area. Home has an open floor plan, a built-in pool perfect for entertaining. Come take a look!!!
